author: gordonsmith
msg: Falcon: Eliminated Javadoc in overview.html referring to a 'fonts' subpackage.

The donated compiler does not support font embedding because font transcoding requires proprietary Adobe technology. You must first transcode the font file to a SWF file using Adobe's command-line fontswf tool; as part of this process you specify a symbol name for the font inside the SWF using the -alias option. You can then embed the transcoded font as a SWF symbol with something like [Embed(source="MyFont.swf", symbol="MyFont")].
